### ============================================
### Web3 链上资产管理系统 - API 接口测试 (含实际测试数据)
### ============================================

### 基础配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### ============================================
### 1. 核心业务接口测试
### ============================================

### 查询充值记录列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/deposit/list?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询提现订单列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/list?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询用户充值历史 (Hardhat 默认账户 #0)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/deposit/user/0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询用户提现历史 (Hardhat 默认账户 #0)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/user/0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266
Accept: application/json

###

### 充值统计数据
GET http://localhost:8080/api/deposit/statistics
Accept: application/json

###

### 提现统计数据
GET http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/statistics
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### 2. 事件监听与系统状态
### ============================================

### 查询事件监听器偏移量
GET http://localhost:8080/api/event-listener/offsets
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询监听状态摘要
GET http://localhost:8080/api/event-listener/status
Accept: application/json

###

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### 3. 动态链配置管理（第六步）
### ============================================

### 查询所有链配置
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chain/list
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询指定链配置详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chain/detail/localhost
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询第二个链配置详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chain/detail/localhost2
Accept: application/json

###

### 添加新链配置（测试用）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chain/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chainName": "test-chain",
  "rpcUrl": "http://127.0.0.1:8547",
  "chainId": 31339,
  "status": 1
}

###

### 启用指定链
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/chain/enable/test-chain
Accept: application/json

###

### 禁用指定链
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/chain/disable/test-chain
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### 4. 合约地址管理（第六步）
### ============================================

### 查询所有合约地址
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contract/list
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询指定链的所有合约地址
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contract/list/localhost
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询第二个链的所有合约地址
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contract/list/localhost2
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询指定链的指定类型合约地址
GET http://localhost:8080/api/contract/address/localhost/deposit_vault
Accept: application/json

###

### 添加新合约地址
POST http://localhost:8080/api/contract/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chainName": "localhost",
  "contractType": "test_contract",
  "contractAddress": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000001",
  "abiVersion": "1.0",
  "status": 1
}

###

### 批量添加合约地址
POST http://localhost:8080/api/contract/batch-add
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "chainName": "localhost2",
    "contractType": "extra_token_1",
    "contractAddress": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000002",
    "status": 1
  },
  {
    "chainName": "localhost2",
    "contractType": "extra_token_2",
    "contractAddress": "0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000003",
    "status": 1
  }
]

###

### 更新合约地址状态
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/contract/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chainName": "localhost",
  "contractType": "test_contract",
  "status": 0
}

###

### ============================================
### 5. 交易测试接口 (Hardhat 本地环境)
### ============================================

### 测试充值（使用配置中的私钥）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test/deposit
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

tokenAddress=0xe7f1725e7734ce288f8367e1bb143e90bb3f0512&amount=1000000000000000000

###

### 测试提现（使用配置中的私钥）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test/withdrawal
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

tokenAddress=0xe7f1725E7734CE288F8367e1Bb143E90bb3F0512&amount=50

###

### ============================================
### 6. ERC20 授权管理测试
### ============================================

### 查询用户授权额度 (ERC20 Allowance)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/allowance?chainName=localhost&userAddress=0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266&tokenAddress=0xe7f1725E7734CE288F8367e1Bb143E90bb3F0512&withdrawContract=0x5FC8d32690cc91D4c39d9d3abcBD16989F875707
Accept: application/json

###

### 模拟用户授权 (Approve)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/approve
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

chainName=localhost&tokenAddress=0xe7f1725E7734CE288F8367e1Bb143E90bb3F0512&privateKey=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80&amount=1000000000000000000

###

### ============================================
### 7. 提现操作测试
### ============================================

### 执行提现 (Withdraw)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/withdraw
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

chainName=localhost&adminPrivateKey=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80&withdrawalId=0

###

### ============================================
### 8. 提现申请与审批测试
### ============================================

### 用户申请提现 (Request Withdrawal)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/requestWithdrawal
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

chainName=localhost&userAddress=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80&tokenAddress=0xe7f1725E7734CE288F8367e1Bb143E90bb3F0512&amount=1000000000000000000

###

### 管理员审批提现 (Approve Withdrawal)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/approveWithdrawal
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

chainName=localhost&adminKey=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80&withdrawalId=0

###

### ============================================
### 9. 提现记录查询测试
### ============================================

### 获取下一个提现ID (Get Next Withdrawal ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/nextWithdrawalId?chainName=localhost
Accept: application/json

###

### 查询提现记录详情 (Get Withdrawal Record)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/withdrawal/withdrawalRecord?chainName=localhost&withdrawalId=0
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### 10. 直接提现测试
### ============================================

### 直接给提现合约打款 (Test Direct Withdraw)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test/directWithdraw
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

tokenAddress=0xe7f1725E7734CE288F8367e1Bb143E90bb3F0512&amount=3000000000000000000

###

